                        <div class="img">
                            <img src="<%= require('assets/images/news/news-list2.jpg') %>" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h5>Anxiety</h5>
                            <div class="desc">
                                <p>Multiple double-blind studies have been conducted indicating that CBD can effectively treat anxiety. Studies using functional magnetic resonance imaging and single-photon emission computed tomography have confirmed the anxiolytic effect of CBD on the brain. These mood-regulating effects of cannabidiol can also be used to treat depression, according to another study conducted on rats. Researchers believe that CBD also has the potential to treat other forms of anxiety disorders such as OCD and PTSD.</p>
