                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="img">
                            <img src="<%= require('assets/images/news/news-list3.jpg') %>" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h5>Psychosis</h5>
                            <div class="desc">
                                <p>A study from 1982 suggests that CBD could inhibit symptoms associated with psychosis. Later that year, it was observed that patients in a South African psychiatric hospital experienced much more frequent psychotic episodes when treated with cannabis low in cannabidiol. There have been additional studies showing how CBD can help reduce psychotic symptoms even in healthy individuals. In 1995, a case study indicated that CBD is also an effective and safe alternative treatment for schizophrenia. This has led researchers to believe that CBD can be instrumental in reducing effects of psychosis.</p>
