                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="img">
                            <img src="<%= require('assets/images/news/news-list4.jpg') %>" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h5>Heart disease</h5>
                            <div class="desc">
                                <p>Further research on the anti-oxidative and anti-inflammatory properties of cannabidiol has shown it to prevent damage from cerebral ischemia, a form of heart disease that can lead to stroke. Additional studies on rodents have demonstrated the significant cardioprotective properties of CBD.</p>
                            </div>
