                        <div class="img">
                            <img src="<%= require('assets/images/news/news-list5.jpg') %>" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h5>Diabetes</h5>
                            <div class="desc">
                                <p>The anti-inflammatory effect of cannabidiol has led scientists to believe that it could be used as a therapeutic agent for the treatment of type 1 diabetes. There have been studies conducted using mice that showed an improvement in diabetic symptoms. In addition, CBD has been observed to attenuate many of the effects of high glucose.</p>
                                <p>ISA Scientific CEO Mark J. Rosenfeld M.S., P.h.D has stated, “Unlike insulin and other existing medications for diabetes, CBD may actually suppress, reverse and perhaps cure the disease.”</p>
                            </div>
