                        <div class="img">
                            <img src="<%= require('assets/images/news/news-list7.jpg') %>" alt=""/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h5>Anti-oxidative <br/>and neuroprotective effects</h5>
                            <div class="desc">
                                <p>A study from the late 1990’s showed how CBD can reduce hydroperoxide-induced oxidative damage. This indicates the potential of cannabidiol to be an effective antioxidant and neuroprotectant. Additional studies have been done suggesting that CBD may also have therapeutic potential for treating symptoms associated with Alzheimer’s and Parkinson’s disease.</p>
