                        </div>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h5>Anti-inflammatory effects</h5>
                            <div class="desc">
                                <p>Multiple reports indicate the anti-inflammatory effect of cannabidiol in mice. The data suggest that CBD could be an effective treatment for arthritis due to its immunosuppressive and anti-inflammatory actions. It has also been found effective in treating sciatic nerve constriction.</p>
                            </div>
